Chest of Jarvonia
Type: Container

A frozen chest found in Jarvonia, cold to the touch.

Chest of Jarvonia is an openable treasury item. It can be received as rewards from Job Boards and Faction Reputation.

Loot Tables

These are the sub-tables for the various materials, coins, and items that can come from these chests.

These treasury items take 4 independent loot rolls when they are opened.
